title.narrative: 1.2. IMMUNIZATION

description.narrative: 1.2 Immunization coverage is scaled up nationally, which contributes to Immunization, Polio Eradication. UNICEF aims to achieve this through Operational Support To Programme Delivery, Systems Strengthening And Institution Building. This contributes to the following Country Programme result: Improved and equitable access to and utilization of quality, high impact mother and child health and HIV interventions results in reduced child mortality and morbidity
